{"tid":2030913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸各位清 星期一升都唔好入市","createTime":"2020-05-23T05:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:35:54.000Z","uid":16406,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e6801f79d7c074bb8c37c6ff42377822fab2d1","tid":2030913,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:21:03.000Z","msg":"我自己一向睇法其實就係熊三<br />\n之前升勢只係未有一個信號去引發跌勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢個信號就出現左<br />\n<br />\n其實唔難見到星期四午市開始大量人已經出緊貨<br />\n收市就放風國安法<br />\n星期五就裂口開再全日下掃<br />\n證明有好多人已經未開市就勁假時段不問價沽貨咁濟<br />\n<br />\n市場永遠係睇未來 係極度樂觀同極度悲觀中搖擺中<br />\n好明顯而家就係極度悲觀 <br />\n<br />\n我睇法係下星期可能會有一兩日升返少少 引人接火棒<br />\n再大幅下掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n524 527見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969e28a49d9ba1403f776299b8555b7e6d54cd6d","tid":2030913,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"咁買d基本面冇變既企業咪平左"},{"pid":"cd981deccae958440f457f839e37f66ef10f642f","tid":2030913,"uid":284595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"mpf走唔走得切"},{"pid":"af6bd997ecf1dc28740e218cca8c6eb16bfc5095","tid":2030913,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969e28a49d9ba1403f776299b8555b7e6d54cd6d","tid":2030913,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"咁買d基本面冇變既企業咪平左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"tencent"},{"pid":"c3b34d640686ae12a40fe35cc71c067654e296dc","tid":2030913,"uid":135661,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cd981deccae958440f457f839e37f66ef10f642f","tid":2030913,"uid":284595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"mpf走唔走得切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"100%北美驚西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj